\par "Is that you, Luke?" he called, knowing full well that no one else would be coming to find him.
\par "Yes sir!" I answered, moving to the voice. "Mom says it's time to quit!"
\par "Oh she does?"
\par "Yes sir." I missed him by one row. I cut through the stalks, and there he was, bent at the waist, both hands moving through the 
